<p>
<b>Textbooks</b><br>
<i>Introduction to Computer Systems: From Bits and Gates to C and Beyond, Second Edition</i>, Yale N. Patt, Sanjay J. Patel<br>
<i>Structured Computer Organization, Fifth Edition</I>, Andrew S. Tanenbaum<br>
</p>

